Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.01,0:00:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這還真是頗有意思的流言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在和平年代發動政變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你才在各支部設施巡查是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是ACCA誕生的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以傳聞才層出不窮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,您認為這僅僅是傳聞?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會在五長官會議上商議這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,現在這個國家是和平的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,ACCA是和平的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.69,0:01:03.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Watch your back, attack is on the way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.57,0:01:05.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,So feel around with the cards you play
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:07.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Lookin' out, suspicion, for they keep deceivin'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:09.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Aim for every minute that you believe is right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:11.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&HDDE2F4&\3c&H000000&\bord1\blur2}Silhouette conspiracies indefinite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:13.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&HDDE2F4&\3c&H000000&\bord1\blur2}Never fool, gotta stay cool. Smoke another cigarette
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:15.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H411C0F&}Whatever you believin' now conflicts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:16.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H411C0F&}Observe every little thing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:19.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF1F2F8&\3c&HF1F2F8&\bord0.5}パズルはtorturing with their eyes (With your eyes!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:21.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF1F2F8&\3c&HF1F2F8&\bord0.5}抗えない奪い合い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:25.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF1F2F8&\3c&H8A919A&\bord1\blur1}Trivial真相を翻すevery noon (Every night, now!)
