Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:30.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE9D1C0&\3c&HE9D1C0&\bord0.5}目の前の全てがSuggestion (Tell me what it says!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF1F2F8&\3c&H000000&\bord1\blur2}Anytime, you'll find what you should know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:34.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF1F2F8&\3c&H000000&\bord1\blur2}Here we go now!
